text: Kandoeng Commune () is a khum (commune) in Bati District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, Kandoeng Commune has 8 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable mw-collapsible" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21020401 |Krasang |ក្រសាំង |- !2 |21020402 |Krang Ampil |ក្រាំងអំពិល |- !3 |21020403 |Aopheasang |ឱភាសាំង |- !4 |21020404 |Preah Mlob |ព្រះម្លប់ |- !5 |21020405 |Trapeang Leuk |ត្រពាំងលើក |- !6 |21020406 |Kandoeng Thum |កណ្ដឹងធំ |- !7 |21020407 |Haknuman |ហនុមាន |- !8 |21020408 |Kandoeng Touch |កណ្ដឹងតូច |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Bati District
